Package: ozymandias
Title: Tools for region- and process-centric analyses of multiple assay types
Version: 0.2
Date: 2015-06-01
Author: Tim Triche, Jr.
Maintainer: Tim Triche, Jr. <tim.triche@gmail.com>
Authors@R: c(person("Tim", "Triche, Jr.", role = c("aut","cre"),
                    email = "tim.triche@gmail.com"),
             person("Steve", "Horvath", role = c("aut", "ctb")))
Description: A pipeline to process and match Illumina DNA methylation data, SNP barcodes, expression and/or SV/CNV/SNV data for subjects who may have "holes"
Depends: minfi, DMRcate, CopyNumber450k, ConsensusClusterPlus, RPMM, WGCNA
Imports: methods, limma, Matrix, matrixStats, rtracklayer, GenomicRanges
Suggests: knitr, RUnit, separationplot, FEM
License: AGPL
VignetteBuilder: knitr
biocViews: GenomeAnnotation, DNAMethylation, FeatureExtraction
